==English==
===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''[[tropical]] [[year]]'''

# The time that it takes for the Sun to return to the same position along the [[ecliptic]], as viewed from the Earth, especially:
# A [[vernal equinox]] year, the time between two [[successive]] [[vernal]] [[equinox]]es.

====Usage notes====
The tropical year is not traditionally calculated between the observational dates of the equinoxes, owing to inaccuracies in the Gregorian as well as earlier calendars.

